reviewText: As it doesn't come out till later this week I'll call it a pre-review. Hopefully this is a sign that next year we might have a Disney Channel Halloween episode dvd. Suite Life, Even Steven, That So Raven are all great series and I'm sure their Xmas holiday specials will be as good as their Halloween ones.
I have just seen this and it looks great, but i'm dying to know if this DVD has any episodes of American Dragon: Jake Long on it. Will anyone who knows PLEASE tell me in a review!!

This DVD is a rare gem;both because it is about Christmas,and it also has Disney Channel characters celebrating Christmas in their own ways.
My daughter loves these older Disney shows and at Christmas we have a tradition of watching all kinds of Christmas programs over and over.

My daughter and I enjoyed this very very much, especially That's so Raven, Even Stevens and Phil of the future episodes.  This is from back when the Disney Channel was good.  It brought back good memories for us.  I really wish they would make all the Even Stevens episodes available.  That was a great show!

If you enjoyed watching any of these shows as a kid you'll love this DVD. It's got the holiday episodes of all my favorite disney channel shows: That's so Raven, Lizzie McGuire, Even Stevens, The Suite Life of Zack & Cody, and Phil of the Future. I'm going to watch this in December!

I wish they would release the Even Stevens seasons on DVD because I would definitely buy it.
Felt like a kid again watching this DVD.  It was a great time watching the old Disney! Definitely watching this in December :)
i love these old shows brings back memories its sad that some of the shows are over but it was nice just to watch old time shows

The main reason I bought this was because of That's So Raven, Even Stevens and Kim Possible.
Those episodes did not disappoint. As for The Suite Life and Lizzie McGuire I did not care much for those.
yes , this  product is what it seems, no skips :) Iam  happy with my purchase ,thank u so much,
Not as good as I wanted it to be since I was trying to bring back memories of my childhood. On the other hand, most of my favorite old shows!

What a weird mix of cartoons and shows.  You may or may not recognize some of these shows.  Not all are really that holiday oriented.  Still worth a few bucks.  Will keep the kids busy for a while during the holiday season.
If you are like myself and enjoy watching the kids shows on Saturday mornings, then you will love this dvd.
I enjoy  dvds for Christmas  its my favorite times of the year .  I like Lizzie Mc Guire .

This is a great addition to your Christmas collection.  The kids will love it.  Contains great episodes of the best Disney shows ever, sure to get you in the Christmas spirit.  Hopefully they will make a Halloween DVD special now.  Highly recommended.
I'm Kim Possible's biggest fan! I got it because It has her in her mission outfit,and she looks the best in it,with her long red hair down.
